{"tid":483396,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[樂仔] 余文樂創瘋狂電競，成立《傳說對決》《英雄聯盟》MAD TEAM 戰隊","createTime":"2017-11-29T05:47:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-01T08:01:09.000Z","uid":12984,"like":11,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"714884e93fd382c5e4be40441fbb114ec8ade49d","tid":483396,"uid":12984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T05:47:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/MadTeam.club/photos/a.295026821007389.1073741829.288554201654651/294768397699898/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FMadTeam.club%2Fphotos%2Fa.295026821007389.1073741829.288554201654651%2F294768397699898%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=wpymXzIE9pr1X%2Be76RV4UAtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=43b1915f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/MadTeam.club/photos/a.295026821007389.1073741829.288554201654651/294768397699898/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n瘋狂電競有限公司 (MAD CREW ESPORT LTD.) 新聞稿<br />\n<br />\n今日在台灣電競娛樂產業有一件喜事要宣佈，「瘋狂電競俱樂部」（MAD TEAM）已於11月29日正式成立，本俱樂部秉持著大家長 余文樂先生對電競的喜愛及堅持，以「瘋狂」做為戰隊的信念與象徵，代表每個人都應該懷著一股對電競熱愛的「瘋癲」與「痴狂」，透過俱樂部的成立及運營，期待將來能孕育出更多與我們一樣，把電競當作畢生最愛的同道中人！<br />\n<br />\n在「瘋狂電競俱樂部」（MAD TEAM）成立後，俱樂部在此要宣布兩支職業電競戰隊的成立，「MAD TEAM傳說對決」戰隊與「MAD TEAM英雄聯盟」戰隊，他們將分別代表「瘋狂電競俱樂部」（MAD TEAM）參加其所屬的職業電競聯賽，兩支戰隊的誕生分別承接了原ahq e-Sports Club電競俱樂部旗下「GCS 傳說對決職業電競戰隊 ahq White」、與「LMS英雄聯盟職業電競戰隊ahq Fighter」，<br />\n希望在開賽之後「瘋狂電競俱樂部」可以為觀眾帶來許多瘋狂又精彩的比賽。<br />\n<br />\n「瘋狂電競俱樂部」（MAD TEAM）的創辦人為國際知名藝人 余文樂先生，他的足跡橫跨影、視、歌各領域，其作品也是大家耳熟能詳，詮釋的角色更是深植人心讓人再三回味。他在事業上的成就及表現，仍不忘初心，懷抱著對遊戲的熱愛與感動，讓他決心要投入電競產業，並成立職業電競俱樂部。余文樂先生說：「遊戲對我來說，從一開始單純的快樂及獲得成就感，到現在已經成為我與人交流，聯繫感情的一種方式，在電子競技的世界沒有誰可以是一定的贏家或永垂不朽，但只要堅持到底，永遠都會有不可思議的奇蹟發生，這也是電子競技讓我深深著迷的地方。」<br />\n<br />\n最後感謝ahq e-Sports Club電競俱樂部，栽培出這群年輕的選手，從今天開始「瘋狂電競俱樂部」（MAD TEAM）就要帶著這群選手，一同瘋狂的在電競的這條路上努力前進，並且希望在不久的將來，可以拿到屬於「瘋狂電競」的第一座冠軍獎盃。<br />\n<br />\n瘋狂電競相關社群：<br />\nMAD TEAM facebook：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/MadTeam.club/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FMadTeam.club%2F&d=wpymXzIE9pr1X%2Be76RV4UAtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=cc042fcd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/MadTeam.club/</a><br />\nMAD TEAM Instagram：<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/madteam_official/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fmadteam_official%2F&d=wpymXzIE9pr1X%2Be76RV4UAtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=350b2679\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/madteam_official/</a><br />\nMAD TEAM Youtube：<a href=\"https://goo.gl/sSTVVv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FsSTVVv&d=wpymXzIE9pr1X%2Be76RV4UAtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=66ad2ac6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/sSTVVv</a><br />\n<br />\n媒體聯繫<br />\nMan<br />\nman@madteam.com.tw<br />\n<br />\n#瘋狂電競俱樂部<br />\n#MADTEAM<br />\n#余文樂<br />\n#傳說對決<br />\n#英雄聯盟<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/24129473_294768397699898_6103389056429161015_n.jpg?oh=d1ea0aa341b276af562d2be3f9cea572&amp;oe=5A8A4D29\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F24129473_294768397699898_6103389056429161015_n.jpg%3Foh%3Dd1ea0aa341b276af562d2be3f9cea572%26oe%3D5A8A4D29&h=1b03276f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a79962f43863e9acbdf59c958bc040826d266c77","tid":483396,"uid":761,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T05:48:14.000Z","msg":"Support"},{"pid":"a07d6cb50b2147d01ae919d12298634c980f3606","tid":483396,"uid":13562,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T05:50:53.000Z","msg":"除非你克服到依個問題"},{"pid":"e0a277d4ef52e0db40d126b78ba9730024c93a8a","tid":483396,"uid":68626,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T05:53:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>除非你克服到依個問題</blockquote><br />\n你無發現自己食兵個陣食得好唔自然咩"},{"pid":"8f7e097f2c92bcbf469e37cf49373cc02cbe4fc0","tid":483396,"uid":106348,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":